          "uuid": "0428abf6-2ff2-4af7-b4ba-6e4397ac878e",
          "text": "In addition, approximately 14% of our leases provide for contingent rental payments between 1% and 15% of the restaurant\u2019s gross sales once certain thresholds are met. We have generally been able to renew our restaurant leases as they expire at then-current market rates. The remaining terms of ground leases range from less than one year to 49 years, including optional renewal periods. The remaining lease terms of our other leases range from less than one year to 56 years, including optional renewal periods.",
